OL,3,CPSNI's 12 weeks to redact Katie
OL,4,CSimpson inquest files
OL,6,FThe PSNI have been granted 12 weeks to
OL,7,Fredact more than 350 files relevant to
OL,8,Fthe inquest into the death of
OL,9,Fshowjumper Katie Simpson.
OL,11,FMs Simpson, 21, from Tynan, Co Armagh,
OL,12,Fdied at Altnagelvin Hospital in
OL,13,FLondonderry almost a week after an
OL,14,Fincident in Gortnessy Meadows,
OL,15,FLettershandoney, Co Derry, on August
OL,16,F3, 2020.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
