OL,3,CPSNI's 12 weeks to redact Katie
OL,4,CSimpson inquest files
OL,6,FPolice originally thought it was a
OL,7,Fsuicide but the following year
OL,8,FJonathan Creswell, the partner of Ms
OL,9,FSimpson's sister, was arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,12,FThe trial of Creswell, 36, for murder
OL,13,Fended in April last year after his
OL,14,Fsudden death.
OL,16,FMs Simpson's death is due to be
OL,17,Fexamined at an inquest by coroner Joe
OL,18,FMcCrisken.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
