PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782503276
OL,3,CPSNI's 12 weeks to redact Katie
OL,4,CSimpson inquest files
OL,6,FA pre-inquest review last year heard
OL,7,Fthere were 352 police files to be
OL,8,Fexamined, with between 25,000 and
OL,9,F29,000 pages, including 44 police
OL,10,Freports, 77 transmission files, a list
OL,11,Fof 165 exhibits, 237 statements and 53
OL,12,Finterview files.
OL,14,FAt Laganside court on Friday, counsel
OL,15,Ffor the coroner Philip Henry KC said
OL,16,Fsome 40-50 files previously deemed
OL,17,Fpotentially relevant had now been
OL,18,Fruled out.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
