PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782503276
OL,3,CPSNI's 12 weeks to redact Katie
OL,4,CSimpson inquest files
OL,6,FHe outlined that parties had been
OL,7,Fprovided with a provisional decision
OL,8,Ffrom the judge on redaction of files
OL,9,Fand that some witness statements had
OL,10,Fbeen taken on the issue.
OL,12,FMr Henry said the judge would have to
OL,13,Fdeal with "relatively complicated law"
OL,14,Fto come to the final decision.
OL,16,FOnce a final decision is relayed to
OL,17,Fparties, it will allow the PSNI to
OL,18,Fcomplete their redaction of documents
OL,19,F` which has been on hold ` and is
OL,20,Fexpected to take 12 weeks.
